<div id="review_2904014277" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2904014277" />
    <a title="Sue K H" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4047077-sue-k-h"><img alt="Sue K H" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1624814479p2/4047077.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2904014277?book_show_action=true">Jul 26, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sue K H" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sue K H" href="/user/show/4047077-sue-k-h">Sue K H</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4047077-sue-k-h?shelf=woman-authors">woman-authors</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4047077-sue-k-h?shelf=pulitzer-s-fiction">pulitzer-s-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4047077-sue-k-h?shelf=pulitzers-to-read">pulitzers-to-read</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2904014277" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13877498944621405498">I loved the first half of this book. It reminded of <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/138089.Their_Eyes_Were_Watching_God' title='Their Eyes Were Watching God by Zora Neale Hurston' rel='nofollow noopener'>Their Eyes Were Watching God</a>. However, the second half was a letdown. It didn&apos;t hold my interest but I pushed through. The ending was pretty good, but many things annoyed me about the path to get there. I&apos;m surprised that this won a Pulitzer. 2.5 stars rounded up. </span>
  <span id="freeText13877498944621405498" style="display:none">I loved the first half of this book. It reminded of <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/138089.Their_Eyes_Were_Watching_God" title="Their Eyes Were Watching God by Zora Neale Hurston" rel="nofollow noopener">Their Eyes Were Watching God</a>. However, the second half was a letdown. It didn't hold my interest but I pushed through. The ending was pretty good, but many things annoyed me about the path to get there. I'm surprised that this won a Pulitzer. 2.5 stars rounded up. </span>
  <a data-text-id="13877498944621405498" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

