      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/274315-scarlet-sister-mary-brown-thrasher-books">Quotes from Scarlet Sister Mary</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
